-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249922/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Ian憑《久別重逢》提名金像獎「最佳新演員」，同名歌曲提名「最佳原創電影歌曲」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6736849c1aafbdadb23d5df8b0c5322e/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_14_48_01.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian憑《久別重逢》提名金像獎「最佳新演員」，同名歌曲提名「最佳原創電影歌曲」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
